**Chief Ibanez:** I hardly blame her. She was shot not even a month ago.

**Dr. Okorie:** I might make a stop to visit her before I leave. In the meantime, do we have any new data?

**Dr. Melbourne:** We might have //something//. Our head archivist finally gave me access to some of Euler's old files, back when he worked here. This was in there.

