**Dr. Melbourne:** Idiots kept trying to schedule it for October. [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/black-autumn-hub Not a] [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/rise-of-the-pit-sloth-hub great time] [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/discordant-anthology-hub of year] [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/nothing-to-fear-hub for us].

**Dr. Okorie:** ...oh.

**Dr. Melbourne:** I don't know //too// much about Saltville. I'm 80% sure it's Briar-class, used to be Camelot or Asphodel before the Impasse happened. I can probably get you in touch with Nexology, but... they're a bit busy.

**Chief Ibanez:** Why?

**Dr. Melbourne:** Well... from what I understand, because 8443 is causing so many anomalies around D.C.... they're considering classifying Washington as a Nexus. Or Capitol Hill, at the very least.

**Dr. Okorie:** //Shit.//
